<plot>A Russian man, ARKADI, departs a train in Berlin. He is met by OTTO and KLAUS, who are to drive him to see "Herr Müller". Instead, Otto and Klaus take Arkadi to a deserted bridge with the intent of stealing the contents of his bag before it is delivered to "The Boss". Neither one is prepared for the "gift" that Arkadi was bringing to Herr Müller.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?139567</url></doc>
